dia (max-width:575.98px){\n   .toggle-content.section-template--19562841374902__collapsible_content_CNM8HX-padding .accordion-flush> .accordion-item{\n      margin-bottom:1.5rem !important ;\n    }\n    .toggle-content.section-template--19562841374902__collapsible_content_CNM8HX-padding .accordion-flush>.accordion-item:last-child{\n      margin-bottom:0 !important;\n    }\n  }\n     @media (min-width:768px){\n      .toggle-content.section-template--19562841374902__collapsible_content_CNM8HX-padding .accordion-flush> .accordion-item:last-child{\n        margin-bottom:0rem !important;\n      }\n    }\n       @media (max-width:767.98px){\n      .toggle-content.section-template--19562841374902__collapsible_content_CNM8HX-padding .accordion-flush> .accordion-item:last-child{\n        margin-bottom:1.5rem !important;\n      }\n    }\n    \n\n   \n</style>\n\n<div class=\"toggle-content color-scheme-0c4e4ae4-dfc4-4f20-8628-bb0485be0a13 gradient section-template--19562841374902__collapsible_content_CNM8HX-padding\">\n  <div class=\" container-fluid \">\n    <div class=\"row \">\n      <div class=\"toggle-content__wrapper  col-12 col-lg-9 mx-auto  \">\n        <style data-shopify=\"\">\n\n\n  .title-container{ margin-bottom:clamp(1.875rem, 1.625rem + 1.25vw, 3.125rem); }\n    @media (min-width: 576px) {\n       .title-container{\n        max-width:90%;\n      }\n   }\n    @media (max-width: 575.98px) {\n       .title-container{\n        max-width:100%;\n      }\n   }\n  \n\n  /* \n     @media (min-width: 576px) {\n      .title-container{\n        max-width:90%;\n      }\n     }\n      */\n  \n</style>\n<div class=\"text-break title-container text-center mx-auto  \"><h2 class=\"mx-auto col-11 col-lg-9 h1\">\n        Where Art Meets Heart\n      </h2><p class=\"mb-0 col-11 col-lg-9 mx-auto \">\n        Find answers to common questions about gallery hours, exhibitions, artwork purchases, and more.\n      </p></div>\n        <div class=\"row row-gap-md-3 row-gap-4\">\n          <div class=\"accordion accordion-flush h-100 sticky-md-top\" id=\"accordion\">\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading1\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_TbLipG\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_TbLipG\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        Do you offer guided tours of the gallery?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse  show \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_TbLipG\" aria-labelledby=\"heading1\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>I do not offer guided tours of galleries. However, I can assist with information and help plan your visit.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading2\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_cnBr6B\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_cnBr6B\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        What are the gallery's opening hours?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_cnBr6B\" aria-labelledby=\"heading2\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>The gallery's opening hours are usually from 10 AM to 6 PM, Tuesday to Sunday. However, please check their website or contact them for the most accurate and up-to-date information.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading3\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_4CRWpi\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_4CRWpi\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        How can I purchase artwork from the gallery?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_4CRWpi\" aria-labelledby=\"heading3\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>You can purchase artwork from the gallery by visiting in person, contacting the gallery directly, or browsing their online store if available. Payment options may include credit cards, bank transfers, or other methods specified by the gallery.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading4\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_pzPQ8x\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_pzPQ8x\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        Do you offer guided tours of the gallery?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_pzPQ8x\" aria-labelledby=\"heading4\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>Yes, we offer guided tours of the gallery. You can inquire about availability and schedule at the front desk or book in advance through our website.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading5\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_HKKGxF\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_HKKGxF\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        Can I take photos of the artwork during my visit?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_HKKGxF\" aria-labelledby=\"heading5\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>Photography policies vary by gallery. Generally, some galleries allow photos without flash, while others may have restrictions. It's best to check with the gallery staff or refer to their guidelines for specific rules.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading6\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_pfwREk\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_pfwREk\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        Hat events or workshops do you offer at the gallery?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_pfwREk\" aria-labelledby=\"heading6\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>The gallery offers a variety of events and workshops, including artist talks, hands-on art classes, and special exhibitions. Check the gallery's website or contact them for a current schedule.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading7\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_HrkEQH\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_HrkEQH\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        Are the exhibitions permanent or temporary?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_HrkEQH\" aria-labelledby=\"heading7\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>Exhibitions at the gallery are typically temporary, with new shows rotating throughout the year. Check the gallery's schedule for specific dates and durations.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n\n\n                <div class=\"accordion-item pt-3 text-break\">\n                  <h2 class=\"accordion-header pb-3\" id=\"heading8\">\n                    <button class=\"accordion-button  collapsed  p-0 bg-transparent text-reset align-items-baseline\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapsecollapsible_row_FEEPAH\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsecollapsible_row_FEEPAH\">\n                      \n\n                      <span class=\"accordion-title h4 mb-0 pe-3 text-reset text-break\">\n                        How do I submit my artwork for exhibition consideration?\n                      </span>\n                    </button>\n                  </h2>\n                  <div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse \" id=\"collapsecollapsible_row_FEEPAH\" aria-labelledby=\"heading8\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-body px-0 pt-0 pb-3\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion__content rte\">\n                        <p>To submit artwork for exhibition, follow the gallery's submission guidelines, which may include a portfolio and application form. Check their website for details.</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              \n</div>\n          \n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n        </main>",
